Jokes about learning Japanese
by furrykef » Fri 08.14.2009 8:07 pm Post 'em here. Here's mine to start with:Guy 1: I've been studying Japanese for a few years now. I wonder how long it'll be before my Japanese is good as my Italian...Guy 2: I didn't know you speak Italian.Guy 1: I don't.
